## Logging Requirements

### Log Entry Structure
```rust
#[derive(Serialize)]
pub struct LogEntry {
    pub timestamp: String,           // ISO 8601
    pub level: String,               // trace/debug/info/warn/error
    pub target: String,              // Module path
    pub message: String,
    pub span: Option<SpanContext>,
    pub fields: HashMap<String, Value>,
}

#[derive(Serialize)]
pub struct SpanContext {
    pub name: String,
    pub trace_id: String,
    pub span_id: String,
    pub parent_span_id: Option<String>,
}
```

### Required Log Points
- [ ] Harness initialization (seed, config)
- [ ] Each scenario step start/end
- [ ] Network events (partition, heal, latency)
- [ ] Time advancement
- [ ] Object creation/retrieval
- [ ] Enforcement decisions (allow/deny)
- [ ] Audit event emission
